{"tid":1634930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美心清盤！！！","createTime":"2019-10-07T10:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T09:36:52.000Z","uid":270153,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"74f64a54629fe63a3803ed530455d636af84b03f","tid":1634930,"uid":270153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:48:06.000Z","msg":"對唔住啱咗你入嚟，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係重要！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想搞大個坐爆Starbucks, 元氣活動，睇睇大家有乜意見！<br />\n活動名稱（有咁好請出聲）:<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">&ldquo;和理&nbsp;hea&quot;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n活動目的: <br />\n1)&quot;和理 hea&quot; 坐 Starbucks <span style=\"color: purple;\">免費飲水</span>，元氣<span style=\"color: green;\">免費飲綠茶食薑</span>，坐下嘆冷氣！（係咪好撚簡單呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n2)瞄準美心，繁忙時間<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊生意</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3)强烈呼籲Starbucks, 元氣<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">取消美心特許經營權</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n適合人仕:<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 和理非</span></span>、學生、OL<br />\n和理hea於繁忙時間，<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">鼓勵慢慢落單改單問長問短，務求排隊趕客、連外買都買唔到!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期時間:&nbsp;（日子時間大家討論，肯做的話日日都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n週日星期二、四繁忙時間&nbsp; 午飯12-2pm、晚飯7-9pm <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">完全</span></span>迫爆佢 <br />\n週末星期六、日 全日 未能出席活動嘅和理非同我<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">迫爆佢</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n活動地點:&nbsp;<br />\n1)美心特許經營&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">Starbucks 星巴克咖啡</span></span>,&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">元氣壽司</span></span><br />\n2)<span style=\"font-size: large;\">美心集團MX</span>, <span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港地</span>, <span style=\"font-size: large;\">can.teen</span>等<br />\n<br />\n活動原因:<br />\n美心創始人女兒伍淑清到聯合國<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"></span>抹黑香港運動為 &quot;騷亂&quot;[/purple]</span>，支持香港政府及<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">警察</span></span>。<br />\n幫襯就梗係要去黃絲啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慢慢坐，做吓嘢，hea吓就梗係去Starbucks丶元氣飲杯水，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">慢慢hea</span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非，用10分鐘食完個晏晝，之後去飲杯水坐下打機啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">呢件事講就講咗好耐，未見過正式做得爆！就係呢幾日內同我推爆佢</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做嘢</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">想美心清盤就做嘢啦屌！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ac6189fc862f1503a826d779a541fb38fa3aff","tid":1634930,"uid":10038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:49:09.000Z","msg":"講左好多次 咪撚做標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3f806e4caf2b47e8f2c8ae052d4e967877d0f9","tid":1634930,"uid":15477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"收皮啦標題撚<br />\n唔撚睇直接block"},{"pid":"566dc6eb3cd28126ae5a3986cad6ee6a606c159f","tid":1634930,"uid":149575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:49:31.000Z","msg":"on99"},{"pid":"b30eb186684b31e108ff486d4b4c3eedc52f9b14","tid":1634930,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:50:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全條街無人戴口罩<br />\n如果和理非連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話抗爭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14fe8c08ffada7d12e502ab39d3c484679967d7e","tid":1634930,"uid":52538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"標題黨blocked <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1158fd3668bc30841764a696723a9eab662d327f","tid":1634930,"uid":163057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:58:02.000Z","msg":"你人定鬼？"},{"pid":"62d721d064ff4edf427101816d0cfec66f12034f","tid":1634930,"uid":136771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"標題黨收皮啦，拉"},{"pid":"3f01ba31e9d101a34920165fcbac872a4f18123c","tid":1634930,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:59:32.000Z","msg":"Block"},{"pid":"f4b61dee7bf2695393edc1a9c48119a9471fd737","tid":1634930,"uid":62151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"假新聞、標題黨<br />\n<br />\n我們發現有部份會員故意發放虛假資訊，捏造假新聞誤導他人。有關情況我們將暫時作出以下實驗性措施：<br />\n<br />\n如用戶發現疑似假新聞內容，請使用「舉報功能」向我們投訴，管理團隊將於確認後將於該主題作出警示。<br />\n在此提醒會員可善用使用不推文回覆減低其主題熱門分數，協助停止傳播錯誤資訊。<br />\n<br />\n注意：由於管理團隊在事實查証方面並非有公信力的機構，亦只能盡量從有限渠道收集資訊，因此部份情況無法準確判斷有關資料真確性，屆時或會於有關主題作出「已收到大量會員反映有關主題的真實性有待確定」警示，如有會員對管理團隊的判斷存疑請向我們反映。另外，如有相關機構願意協助，歡迎隨時聯絡我們。<br />\n<br />\n在此亦請用戶在發表或轉載資料時負責任，盡量附上資料來源或於未經証實的資訊中清晰註明「未經証實」。<br />\n如有用戶為故意或多次發放假新聞故意誤導用戶或嘗試操控輿論，我們將作出禁言警告或永久封鎖處理。<br />\n<br />\n另外，我們亦留意到有個別會員發表與標題完全無關的「標題黨」主題令其他會員反感，我們在此提醒會員避免使用該方式發表主題，如情況持續管理團隊將會考慮進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">[公告] LIHKG 常見問題公告 2019-09-25\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區\nhttps://lih.kg/eecsrT</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a35a70ba9dbf83c27270d855bcfe6a4c792d3a52","tid":1634930,"uid":324892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:00:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"670640b90f645a4341da0c9629181e31bf6b49ed","tid":1634930,"uid":88782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:31:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母標題黨"},{"pid":"8d7465d64e7a3c67df15cd0302c66752987d8718","tid":1634930,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"53cff7d136868a42947990d062ff12886119d69c","tid":1634930,"uid":198783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"標題黨死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e78b8d92ef24c8af62a8acd1b19a59ab21e4883","tid":1634930,"uid":177510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"sorry, 標題黨真係令人會唔想睇內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d06585cfc4b4a4a43f543ca167de10541ef4e23","tid":1634930,"uid":20696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"樓主正on9<br />\n無論你內文幾有內容<br />\n所有人都會睇都唔睇/睇完之後屌你標題黨<br />\n冇人會認真討論<br />\n正一on9仔"},{"pid":"ff12fe40a2ceb9b046bfa86e9ae8e84824f3d1bd","tid":1634930,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"標題黨正PK，講乜都無用。<br />\n睇啲有用嘢好過。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ah.soso.56/videos/10157584175023373/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fah.soso.56%2Fvideos%2F10157584175023373%2F&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn426uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=6b3ae0e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ah.soso.56/videos/10157584175023373/</a>"},{"pid":"ba2286c88d005da94ec487a6be0dcd3e6db3f71d","tid":1634930,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco